    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Drag at the Square Presented by Nova Scotia Spirit Co & 94.1 The Breeze - Staring Lemon from Drag Race: Canada Vs. The World"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p><big><b>Presented by Nova Scotia Spirit Co & 94.1 The Breeze<br>\nStarring Lemon from Drag Race: Canada Vs. The World</b></big></p>\n\n<p> <b>Drag at the Square is Back! </b></p>\n<p>Get ready, New Glasgow! The queens are returning to Glasgow Square Theatre for another unforgettable night of glamour, comedy, and fierce performances — just in time to celebrate Pride Month!</p>\n\n<p>Hosted by the fabulous Bridget Von Snaps, this year's lineup features Halifax drag legends Prochenna Aret and Mya Fox, along with special guest LEMON, crowned winner of Canada's Drag Race: Canada vs. The World!</p>\n\n<p>Expect dazzling looks, high-energy numbers, and unapologetic fun as these incredible performers light up the stage for one spectacular night only. Whether you're a longtime drag fan or new to the scene, this is a must-see summer event!</p>\n\n<p>VIP Meet N' Greet: Includes early access to the venue, a photo opportunity with our stars, reserved seating, and a collectible lanyard.\n</p>\n\n<p><b>16+ Event</b></p>\n\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n</style>\n\n"
      }
    ],
