    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Islandfestiles is a major musical event that celebrates the culture, the sea, and the warmth of island communities. Held on Lamèque Island, it offers a friendly summer atmosphere and has brought together thousands of festival-goers for two consecutive years.</p>"
