    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "\n<p><b>19+ Event </b></p>\n<p><b>Get ready for an unforgettable Ladies Night experience as Magic Male Revue comes to Glasgow Square Theatre on Saturday, May 23.</b><br>\nMagic Male Revue is one of Canada's premier touring male revue shows, known for its high-energy choreography, charismatic performers, and interactive stage performances that keep audiences cheering all night long. Founded by Jeremy Smith, the show has toured across Canada, bringing a fun, polished, and professional ladies-night experience to venues and theatres nationwide.  Guests can expect an exciting evening filled with music, laughter, audience interaction, and unforgettable performances from a talented cast of male entertainers. The show is designed to be fun, flirty, and entertaining while remaining clean, playful, and respectful, making it a perfect night out for birthdays, bachelorette parties, or a girls' night with friends. </p>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n</style>\n\n"
      }
