      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Seen Worse - Stand-Up Comedy with Karim Tuffaha"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>After a successful first show in Halifax, new to the comedy scene, Karim Tuffaha for the very first time brings <b>'Seen Worse'</b> to New Glasgow!</p>\n\n<p>Originally from Lebanon and now living in Canada, Karim shares funny and honest stories about what it's like starting over in a new country. From confusing cultural differences to similarities, his comedy is all about realizing that no matter where you're from... we're actually more alike than we think.</p>\n\n<p>Karim brings a goofy, laid-back style to the stage and loves interacting with the crowd, so no two shows are ever the same. Expect plenty of storytelling, spontaneous moments, and laughs about culture shock, everyday life, and the strange things we all get used to.</p>\n\n<p>Before stand-up, Karim created videos on YouTube, TikTok, and Instagram, and now he's bringing that same energy and personality to the stage.</p>\n\n<p>If you enjoy relatable stories, a bit of crowd work, and comedy that doesn't take itself too seriously, come check out <b>'Seen Worse'</b>.</p>\n\n<p>New Glasgow have you <b>'Seen Worse'</b>?</p>\n\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n</style>\n\n"
      }
    ],
