    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Steph Peaks & Friends"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>It's time to put on those sequins and raise your fives! Steph Peaks is back! June 20th at The Astor!</p>\n\n<p>Get ready for another night of chaos, camp and whole lot of sass! Leave the kids at home and come out to be taken into the world of DRAG! From queens to kings and everything in between! Steph is sure to bring a show that will leave you begging for more! Joining her this year is... Eden Disorder, Jo mama, Proshenna Rhett, Mike Hunt, X and south shores very own Hannibal Lickeder & Ruby Foxglove making the trip home all the way from Ottawa!  </p>"
      }
    ],
